                <h3 class="title">Concept</h3>
                Adobe has been looking to create a tablet-based application to allow teams or group of friends to edit videos using a cloud-based service. Adobe Reel allows you to upload and share assets, create your own reels as well as remake existing videos your friends has posted.
            </figcaption>
        </figure>
    </article>
