            <figcaption>
                <h3 class="title">Mechanic</h3>
                The app is based around three main sections: Assets, Projects and Reels. Group of friends  participating in a project can share assets and organise them into bins.Each of a member can create a reel, comment on other reels and invite their own friends to play.
            </figcaption>
        </figure>
    </article>
</section>

<section id="mechanic" class="page-section project-section">
