            <figcaption>
                <h3 class="title">Cloud based</h3>
                The idea of the aplication was to leverage processing video files to a cloud computing service. Once someone adds new assets to his project, the fiels are being uploaded to serves, which decode and compress footage into different qualities - for work/draft and publishing purposes.
            </figcaption>
        </figure>
    </article>
